{"tid":592883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[港樓呢？]買金防冧市？高盛警告：已無「避險資產」了","createTime":"2018-03-14T14:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T16:43:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9acefbab45c8165b2b2923707727edc650f6a8","tid":592883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，華爾街大行之一高盛發表悲觀報告，<span style=\"color: red;\">預警沒有一項金融資產是「避險資產」！這意味若現時發生環球冧市，全球投資者恐一同輸錢、無得避！</span><br />\n<br />\n傳統上，美國國債、黃金、避險貨幣如日圓及瑞士法郎，均被市場人士認為當金融市場暴冧時，資金會大量流入的「避險資產」。不過，高盛表示，不再是了，將是無處可避！<br />\n<br />\n高盛警告，未來將有兩大原因令到市場震盪！首先是美國聯儲局加息及收緊貨幣政策，當市場廣泛地認定加息僅是開始的時候，巨大震盪就會隨之而來。另一原因是市場已不知不覺間沒有「避險資產」了，理由是俗稱「恐慌指數」的VIX指數向來與股市走勢相反，即VIX指數上升，理應反映市場避險情緒較高，但高盛看到，21項資產中，包括美債、黃金、日圓、瑞士法郎，竟沒有一項與VIX指數呈現同步趨勢，意味市場已步入了「多元化絕望」，即不能因投資組合多元化而逆市贏錢。<br />\n<br />\n高盛解釋，數據顯示，VIX指數與美國標指是80%時間呈現相反走勢，即買VIX指數上升，理應能對沖股市下跌，是最佳「保險」。故此，如果某項資產是「避險資產」的話，理應與VIX指數同上同落，以發揮對沖作用，但現時的事實是：沒有！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180314/bkn-20180314215121908-0314_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180314%2Fbkn-20180314215121908-0314_00842_001.html&d=PCXXq2x%2FEDCv2h6wDdiBy54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a186f445\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180314/bkn-20180314215121908-0314_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"094fd8e54baee865a55b7b3cac46595e45d17033","tid":592883,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:28:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">還有港樓</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7530f80e9eafa96cabafac4a40ab2946d1953f","tid":592883,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"bitcoin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408c8bd1d17c5341d90fea42fcb4b71a2e1fe795","tid":592883,"uid":45213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"快撚d啦"},{"pid":"ea1b76541a226c52825a712338bfa8c4c157a2d7","tid":592883,"uid":35814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"仲有午餐肉，strong hold！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913a3b8b4cfd6b2cd2eea0943ef6fb844f558158","tid":592883,"uid":21063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"一齊輸咁邊個贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefb7960b39d634420b127a97b48c7b872493989","tid":592883,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913a3b8b4cfd6b2cd2eea0943ef6fb844f558158","tid":592883,"uid":21063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"一齊輸咁邊個贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"美國係咁印銀紙邊有人贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e351dc05ac2a52b71489dde5ce451d70580fe9","tid":592883,"uid":22624,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aefb7960b39d634420b127a97b48c7b872493989","tid":592883,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913a3b8b4cfd6b2cd2eea0943ef6fb844f558158","tid":592883,"uid":21063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"一齊輸咁邊個贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"美國係咁印銀紙邊有人贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"中國成最大贏家"},{"pid":"94d93e33911dade41d7d4d4489301d4e6ebe100c","tid":592883,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913a3b8b4cfd6b2cd2eea0943ef6fb844f55815